description: Kenongwo Group US, Inc., through its subsidiary, Jiangxi Kenongwo Technology Co., Ltd., engages in researching, developing, manufacturing, and selling of bamboo charcoal biomass organic, amino acid water-soluble, selenium-rich foliage, and other types of fertilizers in the People's Republic of China. It sells its products through distributors. The company was incorporated in 2018 and is based in Yichun, China.
